community. The move is expected to attract diverse talent and reshape the future of medical education.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/a-93-year-old-widow-gave-1-billion-to-a-bronx-medical-school-and-future-doctors-may-never-see-tuition-bills-again/articleshow/131137151.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/a-93-year-old-widow-gave-1-billion-to-a-bronx-medical-school-and-future-doctors-may-never-see-tuition-bills-again/articleshow/131137151.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T15:32:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131137435,imgsize-40784.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[The isolator helmet: How Hugo Gernsback’s bizarre 1925 invention was designed to block 95% of sound and induce total concentration amongst workers and inventors]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131172162.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/the-isolator-helmet-how-hugo-gernsbacks-bizarre-1925-invention-was-designed-to-block-95-of-sound-and-induce-total-concentration-amongst-workers-and-inventors/articleshow/131172162.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/the-isolator-helmet-how-hugo-gernsbacks-bizarre-1925-invention-was-designed-to-block-95-of-sound-and-induce-total-concentration-amongst-workers-and-inventors/articleshow/131172162.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T15:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131172257,imgsize-397291.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[How your smartphone camera exists because of Albert Einstein: The Nobel-winning 