21.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T11:06:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131167590,imgsize-744754.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scientists stunned after finding the oldest English poem by an agricultural worker inside a medieval manuscript in Rome]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131166681.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/scientists-stunned-after-finding-the-oldest-english-poem-by-an-agricultural-worker-inside-a-medieval-manuscript-in-rome/articleshow/131166681.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/scientists-stunned-after-finding-the-oldest-english-poem-by-an-agricultural-worker-inside-a-medieval-manuscript-in-rome/articleshow/131166681.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T10:45:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131166709,imgsize-48452.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Top 10 happiest cities in US: How Fremont, Scottsdale and Overland Park built happier communities]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131166353.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/top-10-happiest-cities-in-us-how-fremont-scottsdale-and-overland-park-built-happier-communities/articleshow/131166353.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/top-10-happiest-cities-in-us-how-fremont-scottsdale-and-overland-park-built-happier-communities/articleshow/131166353.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-0